query:
INSERT INTO extensions (slug, name, description, version, downloadUrl, price, trialDays, isActive, features) 
VALUES 
  ('parametrix', 'PARAMETRIX', 'Professional Parametric Cladding Layout Generator for SketchUp', '1.0.0', 'https://github.com/mike-ai-lab/parametrix', 4900, 7, true, '["Multi-Face Layouts","Advanced Trimming","Rail Systems","Pattern Control","Preset Management","Single-Row Mode","Professional Components"]'),
  ('autonestcut', 'AutoNestCut', 'Intelligent Cut List and Nesting Optimization for SketchUp', '1.0.0', 'https://github.com/mike-ai-lab/cutlist', 4900, 7, true, '["Automatic Cut List Generation","Intelligent Nesting","Material Management","Export Options","Assembly Viewer","Grain Direction"]')
ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE 
  name = VALUES(name),
  description = VALUES(description),
  version = VALUES(version),
  downloadUrl = VALUES(downloadUrl),
  price = VALUES(price),
  trialDays = VALUES(trialDays),
  isActive = VALUES(isActive),
  features = VALUES(features)
